Package: amdxdna-dkms
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         dkms,
         linux-headers-generic | linux-headers,
Description: AMD XDNA NPU kernel driver and firmware via DKMS
 This package provides the AMD XDNA NPU kernel driver (amdxdna.ko)
 and associated firmware for AMD XDNA accelerators.
 .
 The driver is compiled and installed for your running kernel via DKMS
 (Dynamic Kernel Module Support). This ensures the driver works with
 kernel updates.
 .
 Supported hardware:
  - AMD NPU1 (PCI ID 1502)
  - AMD NPU3 (PCI ID 17f1, 17f2)
  - AMD NPU4 (PCI ID 17f0 Rev 10)
  - AMD NPU5 (PCI ID 17f0 Rev 11)
